By: Casanova
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Hold of Passion
---
The greatest part of my life was spent in trying to make myself ill, and when
I had succeeded, in trying to recover my health. (Now) age. that cruel and
unavoidable disease, compels me to be in good health in spite of myself.
